# cock.li
IMAPAccount firemail
Host mail.cock.li
Port 993
User drot@firemail.cc
PassCmd "pass Email/drot@mail.cock.li"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore firemail-remote
Account firemail

MaildirStore firemail-local
Path ~/.mail/
Inbox ~/.mail/Inbox
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel firemail
Master :firemail-remote:
Slave :firemail-local:
CopyArrivalDate yes
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
